<h1>We'll stop you<br />communicating with the<br />dead, <span>just like that!</span></h1>
<p>Mortascreen, <strong>the UK's most effective</strong> deceased suppression file.</p>
<p>With over 1,500 deaths in the UK every day it's vital that marketing databases are kept up to date to ensure cost-effective campaigns and avoid the negative publicity that mailing the deceased can create.</p>
<p>Mortascreen is the<strong> preferred, proven</strong> and <strong>trusted</strong> choice of direct mailers throughout the UK and <strong>guarantees</strong> you more accurate, comprehensive and <strong>recent</strong> data than any other deceased file.</p>
